sequenceDiagram
    participant OVMS as OVMS<br/>gRPC/REST Handler
    participant Runtime as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>(ov::Core)
    participant Frontend as Frontend<br/>(ONNX/TF/IR/PT/PP/TFL)
    participant Core as OpenVINO Core<br/>(ov::Model graph)
    participant Transforms as Transformation Pipeline<br/>(optimization passes)
    participant Plugin as Device Plugin<br/>(CPU/GPU/Auto)
    participant HW as Hardware<br/>(Intel CPU/GPU)
    participant FS as File System<br/>(model storage)

    Note over OVMS, HW: Flow 1: Model Loading (startup / first request)

    OVMS->>Runtime: ov::Core::compile_model(path)
    Runtime->>Frontend: Select frontend by format
    Frontend->>FS: Read model file<br/>(ONNX/SavedModel/IR XML+bin)
    FS-->>Frontend: Model data (protobuf/flatbuf/XML)
    Frontend->>Core: Parse → ov::Model graph<br/>(ops from opsets 1-13)
    Core-->>Runtime: In-memory model graph

    Runtime->>Transforms: Apply optimization passes
    Note right of Transforms: Constant folding<br/>Precision conversion<br/>Op fusion<br/>INT8/INT4 quantization (LPT)
    Transforms-->>Runtime: Optimized graph

    Runtime->>Plugin: plugin::compile_model()
    Note right of Plugin: CPU: oneDNN + xbyak JIT<br/>GPU: OpenCL kernels
    Plugin-->>Runtime: CompiledModel<br/>(device-specific executable)

    Note over OVMS, HW: Flow 2: Inference Request (per-request)

    OVMS->>Runtime: CompiledModel::create_infer_request()
    Runtime-->>OVMS: InferRequest handle

    OVMS->>Runtime: InferRequest::set_input_tensor(data)
    OVMS->>Runtime: InferRequest::infer()
    Runtime->>Plugin: Execute inference
    Plugin->>HW: Dispatch compute kernels<br/>(oneDNN/OpenCL)
    HW-->>Plugin: Compute results
    Plugin-->>Runtime: Output tensors
    Runtime-->>OVMS: InferRequest::get_output_tensor()
    OVMS-->>OVMS: Return prediction result<br/>via gRPC/REST

    Note over OVMS, HW: All interactions are in-process C++ API calls<br/>No network traffic within OpenVINO
